STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Anthony BARHAM, a/k/a Toney Barham, Anthony Maurice Barham, Jeff Richardson and Maurice Williams, Defendant-Petitioner. C-596 September Term 2018
081615 Supreme Court of New Jersey. March 8, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004920-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
